{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 1213499, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "267801", "body": "Imprisoned in chains, he still says \"[b]speak quickly young one, I have urgent matters to attend[/b]\". Old habits die hard.", "date": "2010-12-08T00:42:29-06:00", "rating": 60, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Judging by the new PTR info, the \"urgent matters\" involve [url=http://www.wowhead.com/blog=183527/patch-4-1-ptr-build-13682-new-and-updated-icons]heading to the Firelands[/url] to get ready for his long-awaited, well-deserved smackdown.  *knock knock*  \"oHAI, Fandral, what's up?  Hey, remember back in the day, how you sent me all over creation for water, weeds, or whatever random crap you wanted at the time, and then acted like I was an annoying moron when I returned with it?  Yeah, maybe you should've thought that through.\"", "creationdate": "2011-02-24T08:37:31-06:00", "id": 227875, "rating": 24, "commentid": 1213499, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "RaevynDarke", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
